# Codecelix Task Manager

A Flutter task management app with Firebase Authentication, Firestore database, and local push notifications for due-date reminders.

## Features
- Email/Password authentication (Register/Login/Logout)
- Add, edit, delete tasks (Title, Description, Due Date, Priority)
- Mark tasks as complete
- Filter tasks by All / Pending / Completed
- Per-user task isolation via Firestore security rules
- Local push notifications for tasks nearing due date

## Tech Stack
- Flutter (latest stable)
- Firebase Authentication
- Cloud Firestore
- Provider (state management)
- flutter_local_notifications

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repo
2. Run `flutter pub get`
3. Add your own `firebase_options.dart` via `flutterfire configure`
4. Run `flutter run`

## Firestore Security Rules
\`\`\`
rules_version = '2';
service cloud.firestore {
  match /databases/{database}/documents {
    match /tasks/{taskId} {
      allow read, update, delete: if request.auth != null && request.auth.uid == resource.data.userId;
      allow create: if request.auth != null && request.auth.uid == request.resource.data.userId;
    }
  }
}
\`\`\`

